-→ ← ↑ ↓ ↔ ↕ ↖ ↗ ↘ ↙ 
-===> <=== =>> <<= ► ◄
-
-Special:
-★ * • ○ ● ◇ ◆ □ ■ △ ▽
-```
-
-### Best Practices
-
-- **Use monospaced characters**: ─ │ ┌ ┐ └ ┘ ┬ ┴ ├ ┤
-- **Keep diagrams compact**: max 20-25 lines
-- **Use consistent spacing** and alignment
