-```json
-{
-  "main": "dist/electron/main/main.js",
-  "scripts": {
-    "build:desktop": "electron-vite build",
-    "dev:electron": "node scripts/dev-electron.js"
-  }
-}
-```
-
-### 2.3 Create Dev Workflow Script
-
